  icon: {fileID: 0}
  iconBackgroundImage: {fileID: 0}
  description: 'With your new weapon and suit of armor, and proven experience as
    a Zombie killer, I think you are ready for active duty!


    Our mission was
    to investigate a large buildup of Goblins in the area.  We thought they were
    preparing for war against us, but it seems they were just defending themselves
    from the undead.


    Maybe if we can take care of the undead threat, the Goblins
    will return home.


    Report to Ser Invyncible to see how you can help.'
